'''硫化亚铬'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]]为CrS。
==化学性质==
硫化亚铬在空气中加热容易被氧化，产生非整比的氧硫化铬、氧化铬(III)等物質。<ref>V. I. Berezanskaya, V. A. Lavrenko, A. P. Pomytkin, ''et al.'' [http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2FBF00794598 High-temperature oxidation of chromium (II) sulfide in air] {{Wayback|url=http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2FBF00794598 |date=20160304233347 }}. Soviet Powder Metallurgy and Metal Ceramics. 1991. 30(11), pp 945-948</ref>
